{"tid":1387121,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"勝者為王 敗者為寇 [共產黨事例］","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:44:11.000Z","uid":191139,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8b641fc3129e1eb6fbdb7197e62e3335c1a2aad9","tid":1387121,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:00:12.000Z","msg":"呢句說話真係聽得多，但各位有包袱嘅有冇認真諗過呢句說話？<br />\n<br />\n1921年中國共產黨成立，於1949年與國民黨內戰最終共產黨得最後勝利，隨後共產掌權，成立<span style=\"color: red;\">新中國</span>。共產黨執政後文革思想要跟哂佢個套，共產黨的暴政暴行都被其他吹捧共產的訊息遮蓋，全因一句：<span style=\"color: red;\">勝者為王 敗者為寇</span> 呢句千古不變的定律，簡單黎講唔理你係邊一派一黨，最後打贏的勝利者先有最後的話事權。<br />\n<br />\n想講比一啲怕擔心有案底有前途的抗爭者知，你地最後打勝仗，所謂的後遺症都可以被消除，甚至可以酌情處理<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;因暴動罪而入獄有案底&quot;</span>，唔擔心會影響前途。<br />\n<br />\n我老豆係典型盲撐政府警察的人，剛才見到佢睇支那劇片尾曲<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;沒有共產黨就沒有新中國，共產黨為各人民謀取最好的&quot;</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到係真係覺得好好笑，但呢個係真：勝者為王 敗者為寇！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"1079dd663e97bc8cd0c5b653138451d7c6b85b3e","tid":1387121,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"69493efa340db661b31d40ad27ba245149b498ce","tid":1387121,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"推啊推"},{"pid":"ac31cf173322c431ab391ef196261b66070a65f7","tid":1387121,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:42:55.000Z","msg":"又一推"},{"pid":"1d9c3c9cf2521fb40561d37eeb153a7f208fae01","tid":1387121,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:43:08.000Z","msg":"推完又再推"},{"pid":"fffb4a759d0dc2868f9cc0cabf6d971c43ecb5a2","tid":1387121,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"推極都仲有"},{"pid":"498817a7ad8d03a491b8cacd2ef3c18513030ba3","tid":1387121,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"好帖不推嗎"}]}